offset means space chodna   row me 12 col ka grid hota hai hum content or col kitni grid column ko chod k likhna chahte hai vo offset k through hota
hai suppose offset-md-4  means medium size me 4 column ka space chod k value likhi jaye
ab isme kya hoga medium screen s sari upper wali class jese large extra large pr yeh offset kam krega but niche wali small extra small inpr kam nhi krega
agr offset-5; likh du toh yeh offset htega nhi
offset-xl-*
offset-lg-*
offset-md-*
offset-sm-*
* means grade from 1 to 12 col 

